---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Flight School Planning Tools | Flight School Friend"
  description="Practical planning tools for estimating flight training costs and choosing what to do next before you spend thousands on flight school."
>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Flight School Planning Tools</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">Practical planning tools for estimating cost and choosing what to do next before you spend thousands on flight school.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Start with the cost calculator or take the decision quiz if you are not sure what to use first.</p>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl text-lg transition shadow-md">Start Here</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/" class="block bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 hover:border-sky-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
        <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Live</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Flight School Decision Tool</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Get a personalized starting path based on your goal, budget, timeline, schedule, medical readiness, and confidence level.</p>
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Use the Decision Tool &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/tools/flight-school-cost-calculator/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-sky-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
        <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Live</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Flight School Cost Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Estimate aircraft, instructor, checkride, gear, and monthly training costs before choosing a flight school.</p>
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Use calculator &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 text-center shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">More tools are coming.</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">Research scorecards, progress tracking, and checkride planning tools will appear here after they are ready for public use.</p>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition">Get a recommended starting path</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
